    <p>{`The bird game object needs to know where the player is. It's known as path finding.`}</p>
    <p>{`Unity makes path finding very easy.`}</p>
    <p>{`With the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`Nav Mesh Agent`}</inlineCode>{`, you can set the following for the bird:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{}}>{`Speed: 5
Angular Speed: 720
